data.description: Nestled within the picturesque Crowne Hill community of Temecula, this exceptional 4-bedroom, 3-bath pool home presents an enticing blend of style, sustainability, and unbeatable location. Set on a coveted corner lot, this residence boasts numerous desirable features, including refinished cabinets, paid solar panels, and proximity to top-rated schools, shopping destinations, and the renowned Temecula wine country.  As you approach this inviting abode, you'll be immediately charmed by its attractive exterior and maintained landscaping. The curb appeal sets the stage for the warmth and elegance that await you inside.  Step through the front door into a well-appointed living space that effortlessly combines comfort and functionality. The refinished cabinets in the kitchen add a touch of sophistication to the heart of the home, while modern appliances and an expansive countertop create an inviting space for cooking and entertaining. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living and dining areas, making it perfect for family gatherings and hosting friends. Additional space downstairs, possible NEXT-GEN suite.   A highlight of this property is the outdoor oasis. The sparkling pool beckons on warm California days, providing a refreshing retreat for relaxation and recreation. Whether you're soaking up the sun on the pool deck or enjoying an evening barbecue in the outdoor entertainment area, this backyard is a haven of outdoor living.  The home features four spacious bedrooms, including a master suite that serves as a private sanctuary. The en-suite bathroom offers all the amenities you need for relaxation, ensuring your comfort and privacy.  With the installation of paid solar panels, you'll not only enjoy lower utility bills but also contribute to a more sustainable future. This environmentally-conscious feature adds tremendous value to the home.  Location-wise, this property is a dream come true. It's situated within close proximity to top-rated schools, making it an ideal choice for families. Nearby shopping centers ensure that daily errands are convenient, while the allure of Temecula's world-class wine country is just a short drive away. Explore a wealth of award-winning wineries, indulge in vineyard tours, and savor culinary delights in this thriving wine region.
